{
  "stem": "3524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know how many patients there were until I read a unit history, and I found out that we had somewhere in excess of 900 patients throughout those four hospitals.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we tried to give them the basic medical needs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Most of it was diarrhea, lung conditions, and severe coughing and malnutrition were the primary reasons they couldn't move and couldn't get back to their homeland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly by sign language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, probably, the most dramatic one I can remember how we adapted to the sign language figure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had one-- I think he was a French doctor-- came in and was asking for some medical supplies, and we were unable to pass the barrier to determine just exactly what he needed until he began to hold his stomach and he went-- And we determined that he was in need of something to control the diarrhea that was prevalent in the area.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in reasonably good supply.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember where we got restocked from, but we had in our stock, in our basic stock, a 55-gallon drum of pure grain alcohol, from which we made our own paregoric and bismuth combinations to treat the diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we also made our own terpin hydrate and codine to act as an expectorant and cough sedative for those who had severe lung conditions.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a-- we were able to make gallons and gallons of that from our initial stock that we had never touched.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our unit had never really taken any-- from the time we hit Europe, we never took any American [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] patients per se.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It turned out that we ended up treating concentration camp internees and displaced persons primarily.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You mentioned there were over 900 patients in these hospitals.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
